><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/deals-signed-by-italy-china-after-pm-melonis-trip-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>跳水——中国选手全勇夺得女子10米跳台金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-wins-gold-womens-10m-platform-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国选手权红婵周二在女子10米跳台比赛中夺冠，为中国在巴黎奥运会上夺得第五枚跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-wins-gold-womens-10m-platform-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>排球-土耳其力压中国队首次进入半决赛，美国队和巴西队晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/volleyball-turkey-edge-china-reach-first-semi-final-brazil-also-through-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，欧洲冠军土耳其队在一场拉锯战中以3-2击败中国队，首次进入奥运会女排半决赛，而美国队则直落两盘击败波兰队晋级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/volleyball-turkey-edge-china-reach-first-semi-final-brazil-also-through-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>市场监管机构称特斯拉将在中国修理170万辆汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-17-mln-vehicles-china-says-market-regulator-2024-08-06/</link><description>国家市场监管机构周二表示，特斯拉正在通过无线软件更新对中国 170 万辆汽车进行远程召回。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-17-mln-vehicles-china-says-market-regulator-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称中国将加强对芬太尼化学品的监管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</link><description>白宫周二表示，中国表示将开始对三种用于制造非法芬太尼的化学品的生产加强控制和监管，称此举“向前迈出了宝贵的一步”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:34:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利的梅洛尼表示，她带女儿去中国为母亲们树立了榜样</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利总理梅洛尼表示，带七岁女儿对中国进行正式访问树立了良好榜样，有助于促进职业母亲的权利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>线上券商富途、UP Fintech暂停美股夜盘交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</link><description>以帮助中国投资者购买全球股票而闻名的在线券商富途控股和UP Fintech Holding已告诉客户，在全球市场波动加剧后，美国股票的夜盘交易将于周二暂停。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动推出 AI 视频应用程序，加入 OpenAI Sora 竞争对手行列</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</link><description>字节跳动扩大了其可根据文本提示生成视频的软件产品范围，加入了越来越多的中国科技公司的行列，进入了ChatGPT创建者OpenAI也瞄准的新兴市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>Zalando 将在中国开设科技网站；目前没有进入市场的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</link><description>Zalando 周二表示，将在中国科技中心深圳开设一个新的科技网站，但目前不打算将其市场扩展到中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着关税的临近，记号笔制造商纽厄尔将更多业务从中国转移</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</link><description>记号笔制造商纽厄尔品牌公司（Newell Brands）首席执行官克里斯·彼得森（Chris Peterson）在接受路透社采访时表示，由于美国总统大选前面临关税的“不确定性”，纽厄尔品牌公司正在将部分厨房用具的生产迁出中国，并将其书写业务的生产迁至田纳西州。 。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>华为与北京汽车推出首款联合开发的电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国科技集团华为和北京汽车周二推出了首款联合开发的电动汽车（EV）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利消息人士称，中国东风汽车有望在意大利建汽车厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利知情人士周二表示，意大利政府与中国东风汽车集团关于在意大利建设汽车工厂的谈判已进入后期阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:46:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>